Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: fsl_sai: Fix channel swap issue on i.MX8MP
Date: Mon, 18 Dec 2023 17:28:51 +0800
Message-Id: <1702891731-3417-1-git-send-email-shengjiu.wang@nxp.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.7.4
